Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.01,Default,Flying Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.08,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,It's spewing fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.43,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard their fire-related organs \Nhad become vestigial!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.78,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.25,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,It's an atavism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:12.97,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,It's become like the dragons \Nyou'd read about in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:25.21,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, he can still go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.69,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:28.11,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,He has a place to go home to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.28,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Please, teach me how to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:42.37,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Your selfish requests \Nare never for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.31,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.63,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.70,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.52,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,First, touch the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.95,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can absorb its magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.79,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll absorb that \Nbefore your body breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:16.72,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:19.86,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.42,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to draw the dragon's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:24.80,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.48,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.56,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:36.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.72,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Merituuli!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.56,Default,Angry Gremlin Alien,0000,0000,0000,,You naughty boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:49.20,Default,Angry Gremlin Alien,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.70,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.11,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.32,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,By the base of its neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.22,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,There's a powerful flow there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.38,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,It's trying to go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.22,Default,More Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Merituuli, distract it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.37,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.87,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.14,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.62,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.25,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:58.72,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.77,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.66,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Elias!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.08,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:09.97,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.32,Default,AA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.60,Default,BB,0000,0000,0000,,The moon looks odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.43,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.08,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, how's Elias?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.57,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Singed, but he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.47,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.42,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,The river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.43,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.66,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come with me, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.28,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Go get the others and then come get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.64,Magus-Internal/narrator,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, you better not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:46.87,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:50.85,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.56,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.13,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.09,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.15,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.90,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:42.22,Default,Craycray,0000,0000,0000,,To think it escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.22,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Shannon-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.22,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.75,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.57,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.15,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.66,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.76,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,It might be tight, but don't take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:24.68,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's going to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.25,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.25,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.80,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.44,Default,Flying Lizard,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you reek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.94,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,She beat you to her, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:47.24,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do the same to my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.66,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to try to do\N everything by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.55,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,I already gave {\i1}him{\i0} an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.27,Magus-Internal/narrator,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.64,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,How's the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.20,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,And the other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.27,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.44,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon is sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.56,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:19.07,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, are you burned or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:26.66,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,You don't realize you're in \Nworse shape than I am, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.48,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:30.92,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.96,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, I can't let that lousy \Nexplainer explain, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.30,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Lindel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.68,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.91,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,I've forced you into an unenviable role.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:43.93,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.64,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I only did it because I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.18,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,That's why this is so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.35,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,You've been cursed by the dragon's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.09,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.82,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to fester in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.03,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,It'll attack, torment, and hex you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.77,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,No human body could contain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.59,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later, your body will fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.01,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,How long will this body last?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.13,Magus-Internal/narrator,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.60,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.54,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:42.87,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived with two curses so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.24,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I was forced to live with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.33,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,One is this, my Sleigh Beggy body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.08,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,The other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:11:01.34,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I live, it'll \Nprobably never leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:10.19,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Taking on one more doesn't\N seem like such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.33,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.73,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,He's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.19,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's him angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.69,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.94,Default,Ancient Skype,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask you to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.86,Magus-Internal/narrator,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.15,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,This is proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:39.37,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,That I was able to think of \Nsomeone other than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.94,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,You do have the option of \Nliving on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.44,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.65,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.68,Default,Doomslap,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:50.83,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.81,Default,Doctor Why,0000,0000,0000,,You may cease to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.90,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.93,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:11.04,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should be out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.90,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell anyone, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.16,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the air outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.43,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.09,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:35.46,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Since you tried to leave from the window \Nand flipped around in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.46,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,That's from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.44,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,My puppy seems to have lost her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.10,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I was just pretending to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.32,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:54.59,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten to let me know when\N you go out, yet you're still well-spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.82,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you didn't reply to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.99,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I was straightening things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.28,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,All day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:05.16,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.98,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,You always try to go somewhere by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:19.86,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you always offer \Nme your hand and grip back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.11,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you ask me to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:30.25,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you're going to \Nleave me, just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.50,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm going to die right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.05,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.32,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,How was I so optimistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:43.69,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen to you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:47.69,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stopped you, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.46,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:56.31,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still thinking that you're always going\Nto be in that home, going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.53,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,That you would manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.71,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.06,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.91,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,At first, we were only using each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.07,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought this would happen \N just because we were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:16.51,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Before this, I was sure I didn't want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.41,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,But so many people helped me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:27.32,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,and I found out that even I could do things \Nthat are worth being thanked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.84,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just waiting for someone \Nto tell me I'm welcome to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.09,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I started {\i1}wanting{\i0} to stay and\N {\i1}wanting{\i0} to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.44,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.83,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,You think that by destroying yourself, \Nyou can earn the right to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.16,Default,Dogger,0000,0000,0000,,E-Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.38,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.44,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.53,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I only did what I did because I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.04,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying, it's just that \Nthere are some things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.00,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,about humans that we don't \Nunderstand ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.83,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:11.19,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, your puppy is a stupid one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.27,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Her body seems to act before her mind thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:24.22,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Elias, will you help this idiot think of a way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the two of us can stay\Nnext to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.86,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the same ability to \Ntake action that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.82,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can go find out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.59,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.62,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:51.43,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,We have to think
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.75,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,of a way to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.43,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:02.73,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mariel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.74,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Goatherder Mariel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.68,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what they call a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.31,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,A transaction at the auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.08,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:16.30,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,I asked for the dragon's blood\N in exchange for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.28,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like that'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.60,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.08,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,You... Your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.88,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.69,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,You're so overprotective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:35.87,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Mariel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.06,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Gleaming goddess of the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:47.39,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,snake-shredding god of storms...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:54.97,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Lend us your hand, your eyes, \Nfor the batting of an eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.95,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.50,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,It's so creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.59,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.75,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have any interest \Nin becoming a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.90,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Witches specialize in curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:38.90,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,If you become one of us—if you join our \Ncoven—we might be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.11,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:45.25,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have the confidence to \Ntell a woman what to do with her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:52.74,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Mariel-san, what do I need \Nto do to become one of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.00,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.58,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, join our gathering as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.89,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.81,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Open that when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.31,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be awaiting your reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.87,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.08,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.33,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.33,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.12,Default,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Such a young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.35,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.32,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,A card?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.42,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,It's an invitation to my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.71,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,When's yours, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.43,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.25,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.01,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where's your party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.18,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you holding a party for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.81,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Par... tay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.41,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.82,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.85,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,You better come up with some plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.18,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.10,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.83,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I feel nauseous all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.30,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the washroom, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.32,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I just came to give you the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.84,Default,Younger,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.55,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Chise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:29.59,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,All this, just as I'd decided \NI don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.91,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join the witch's gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.07,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:44.25,Magus-Flashback,Goatlady,0000,0000,0000,,Your apprentice might not \Nmake it through the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.19,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:51.25,Default,Edgelady,0000,0000,0000,,What matters more is to \Ntake care of your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.82,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.03,0:22:01.37,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think about my party next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.14,Default,Craycray,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon's curse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:20.26,Default,Craycray,0000,0000,0000,,Between my curse keeping me from dying, \Nand your curse leading you to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:23.42,Default,Craycray,0000,0000,0000,,Things might work out pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:24:00.17,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,The reality presented at the witches' \Ngathering was a cruel one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:04.95,Default,Cheeee,0000,0000,0000,,The mage sets out to save the girl, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:09.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that can replace \Na life is another life.
